OL,3,CHundreds of hens rescued from
OL,4,Cslaughter and re-homed as pets
OL,6,FHundreds of battery hens are starting
OL,7,Ftheir retirement after being rescued
OL,8,Ffrom slaughter and re-homed.
OL,10,FThe hens had spent their lives at a
OL,11,Fcommercial egg farm, were collected
OL,12,Ffrom Nottingham on Sunday 15 March,
OL,13,Fand brought to Kirkham, Lancashire, by
OL,14,Fvolunteers from the British Hen
OL,15,FWelfare Trust.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
