OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773681068
OL,3,CHundreds of hens rescued from
OL,4,Cslaughter and re-homed as pets
OL,6,FThe charity say after 18 months, hens
OL,7,Fstill lay eggs but the rate slows, so
OL,8,Ffarmers send them to be killed. Those
OL,9,Frescued will live out their retirement
OL,10,Fin gardens and allotments across the
OL,11,FNorth West.
OL,13,FSimon Dagger, Lancashire co-ordinator
OL,14,Ffor the British Hen Welfare Trust
OL,15,Fsaid: "We've collected around 550 hens
OL,16,Ftoday.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
