PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773681068
OL,3,CHundreds of hens rescued from
OL,4,Cslaughter and re-homed as pets
OL,6,F"The Trust pays the farmer a bit more
OL,7,Fthan they would get it the hens went
OL,8,Fto slaughter, so we just collect
OL,9,Fthousands from around the UK to the
OL,10,Fdifferent distribution centres.
OL,12,F"People come from all over to give
OL,13,Fthem a home."
OL,15,FCarol Johnson from Failsworth in
OL,16,FManchester has re-homed lots of hens.
OL,17,FShe said they make "great pets" and
OL,18,Fare "brilliant for the allotment".
OL,20,FCarol Johnson came from Manchester to
OL,21,Fadopt the hens
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
