OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773681068
OL,3,CHundreds of hens rescued from
OL,4,Cslaughter and re-homed as pets
OL,6,FEirian Roberts is a volunteer for the
OL,7,FBritish Hen Welfare Trust.
OL,9,FShe said: "You don't have to do much
OL,10,Fwith them, they're really great pets.
OL,12,F"They each have their own
OL,13,Fpersonalities. They're really precious
OL,14,Fto us."
OL,16,FAndy Hill at the British Hen Welfare
OL,17,FTrust, said: "People are often
OL,18,Fsurprised by how much joy hens bring.
OL,26,@yD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
