PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773681068
OL,3,CHundreds of hens rescued from
OL,4,Cslaughter and re-homed as pets
OL,6,F"They're funny, curious little
OL,7,Fcharacters, they love routine, and
OL,8,Fthey're genuinely a delight to care
OL,9,Ffor. Plus, they're still more than
OL,10,Fhappy to pop out the occasional egg.
OL,12,F"With spring finally here, this is the
OL,13,Fideal time to start. These girls are
OL,14,Fmore than ready for a fresh beginning,
OL,15,Fand they really do make wonderful
OL,16,Fpets."
OL,26,@tD@AOU
